Subject: [PATCH 319/355] dt-bindings: display: renesas: lvds: Document
 r8a774a3 bindings

Document the RZ/G2M v3.0 (R8A774A3) SoC and and update name for RZ/G2M v1.3
 (R8A774A1) in the LVDS bindings.

Signed-off-by: Khoi Nguyen <khoi.nguyen.aj@renesas.com>
---
 Documentation/devicetree/bindings/display/bridge/renesas,lvds.txt | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/display/bridge/renesas,lvds.txt b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/display/bridge/renesas,lvds.txt
index 5b9d0fe..6399c77 100644
--- a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/display/bridge/renesas,lvds.txt
+++ b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/display/bridge/renesas,lvds.txt
@@ -8,7 +8,8 @@ Required properties:
 
 - compatible : Shall contain one of
   - "renesas,r8a7743-lvds" for R8A7743 (RZ/G1M) compatible LVDS encoders
-  - "renesas,r8a774a1-lvds" for R8A774A1 (RZ/G2M) compatible LVDS encoders
+  - "renesas,r8a774a1-lvds" for R8A774A1 (RZ/G2M v1.3) compatible LVDS encoders
+  - "renesas,r8a774a3-lvds" for R8A774A3 (RZ/G2M v3.0) compatible LVDS encoders
   - "renesas,r8a774b1-lvds" for R8A774B1 (RZ/G2N) compatible LVDS encoders
   - "renesas,r8a774c0-lvds" for R8A774C0 (RZ/G2E) compatible LVDS encoders
   - "renesas,r8a774e1-lvds" for R8A774E1 (RZ/G2H) compatible LVDS encoders
